  "description": {
    "zh": "准备好制造点Chaos了吗？\n化工厂现在已经是真正无法无天之地了，现在该清理垃圾了。\n\n既然你已经把工厂的那个疯子吓跑了并拿走了他的装备，你可以假扮成他来吓唬那里的人。穿上他的装备，使用他的武器。我可以帮你列个装备清单，然后制造混乱。当地人可能会察觉到有些不对劲，所以不要指望他们真的认为你是自己人。别忘了带回你杀的PMC的狗牌。我等你的好消息。\n\nTagilla的装备：\n - AA-12 Gen 1 或 Saiga-12K 或 AKS-74UN 或 MP-155 或 RPK-16\n - Tagilla的\"UBEY\"电焊面罩 + BOSS鸭舌帽 组合 或 Atomic Defense CQCM防弹面罩（黑色）\n - Crye Precision AVS护甲板（Tagilla特别版）/ Strandhogg护甲板",
    "en": "Ready to cause some chaos now?\nThe chemical factory is a truly lawless place, time to clean it up a little.\n\nNow that you scared of this factory maniac and stole his loadout you can scare the shit of the and operators there. Dress up as him, use the same weapons, I can make a list for you for that, and then cause some mayhem. Bandits might know that something seems off, so don't expect that you are actually one of theirs. And bring me the dogtags of the PMC operatives you got rid off. I'll hear from you.\n\nTagilla's Gear :\n - AA-12 / Saiga-12K / AKS-74U / MP-155 / RPK-16\n - Tagilla Welding Mask combined with BOSS Cap or just Atomic Defense CQCM Ballistic Mask\n - Crye Precision AVS Plate Carrier ( Tagilla Edition ) / Strandhogg Plate Carrier"
  },
